description: This file declares API functions and constants for managing GRE interface objects within a Cisco-specific Data Model Library. It includes function prototypes for CRUD operations, parameter accessors, validation, commit, and rollback of GRE interface entries, as well as statistical data retrieval.

methods.name: CGreIf_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns the total number of GRE interface entries.

methods.name: CGreIf_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves a handle to a GRE interface entry by index.

methods.name: CGreIf_AddEntry
methods.description: Creates a new GRE interface entry and returns its handle.

methods.name: CGreIf_DelEntry
methods.description: Deletes the specified GRE interface entry.

methods.name: CGreIf_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves an integer parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets an unsigned long parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets an integer parameter value for a GRE interface.

methods.name: CGreIf_Validate
methods.description: Validates the current configuration of a GRE interface before commit.

methods.name: CGreIf_Commit
methods.description: Applies staged changes to the GRE interface configuration.

methods.name: CGreIf_Rollback
methods.description: Reverts uncommitted changes to the GRE interface configuration.

methods.name: CGreIfStat_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves statistical unsigned long data for a GRE interface.
